#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/transform/smooth.rst:17
msgid ""
"This tool smooths the selected vertices by averaging the angles between "
"the faces. After using the tool, options appear in the *Tool Shelf*:"
msgstr ""
"该工具通过对拉平面之间的夹角，来平滑选中顶点。使用该工具后， *工具栏* 将"
"显示下面的选项:"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/transform/smooth.rst:20
msgid "Number of times to smooth"
msgstr "平滑次数"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/transform/smooth.rst:21
msgid "The number of smoothing iterations."
msgstr "平滑的迭代次数。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/transform/smooth.rst:23
msgid "Axes"
msgstr "轴"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/transform/smooth.rst:23
msgid "Limit the effect to certain axes."
msgstr "限制为仅作用于特定轴向。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/transform/smooth.rst:30
msgid "Mesh before smoothing."
msgstr "平滑前的网格。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/transform/smooth.rst:35
msgid "Mesh after one smoothing iteration."
msgstr "一次平滑后的网格。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/transform/smooth.rst:40
msgid "Mesh after ten smoothing iterations."
msgstr "10次平滑迭代后的网格。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/transform/smooth.rst:42
msgid "Subdividing"
msgstr "细分"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/transform/smooth.rst:44
msgid ""
"Adjusting the *smooth* option after using the :doc:`Subdivide </modeling/"
"meshes/editing/subdividing/subdivide>` tool results in a more organic "
"shape."
msgstr ""
"在使用 :doc:`细分 </modeling/meshes/editing/subdividing/subdivide>` 工具"
"后调整 *光滑度* 选项可以获得更加圆润的形状。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/transform/smooth.rst:48
msgid "Smooth Modifier"
msgstr "平滑修改器"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/transform/smooth.rst:50
msgid ""
"The :doc:`Smooth Modifier </modeling/modifiers/deform/smooth>`, which "
"can be limited to a *Vertex Group*, is a non-destructive alternative to "
"the Smooth tool."
msgstr ""
":doc:`平滑修改器 </modeling/modifiers/deform/smooth>` 是另一种非破坏性的"
"平滑工具，可以限制仅作用于单个 *顶点组*。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/transform/smooth.rst:55
msgid "Laplacian Smooth"
msgstr "拉普拉斯平滑"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/transform/smooth.rst
msgid "Menu:     :menuselection:`Specials --> Laplacian Smooth`"
msgstr "菜单:     :menuselection:`专用项 --> 拉普拉斯平滑`"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/transform/smooth.rst:63
msgid ""
"See the :doc:`Laplacian Smooth Modifier </modeling/modifiers/deform/"
"laplacian_smooth>` for details."
msgstr ""
"详情可参考 :doc:`拉普拉斯平滑修改器 </modeling/modifiers/deform/"
"laplacian_smooth>`。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/transform/smooth.rst:65
msgid ""
"Laplacian smooth is uses an alternative smoothing algorithm that better "
"preserves larger details and this way the overall shape of the mesh. "
"Laplacian smooth exists as a mesh operation and as a non-destructive "
"modifier."
msgstr ""
"拉普拉斯平滑使用另一种平滑算法，可以更好地保留大的细节和网格的大致形状。"
"拉普拉斯平滑除网格操作外，还有对应的非破坏性修改器。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/transform/smooth.rst:69
msgid "Real Smoothing versus Shading Smoothing"
msgstr "真实平滑 VS 着色平滑"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/transform/smooth.rst:71
msgid ""
"Do not mistake this tool with the shading smoothing options described "
"at :doc:`this page </modeling/meshes/editing/smoothing>`, they do not "
"work the same! This tool modifies the mesh itself, to reduce its "
"sharpness, whereas *Set Smooth* / *AutoSmooth* and co. only control the "
"way the mesh is shaded, creating an *illusion* of softness, but without "
"modifying the mesh at all..."
msgstr ""
"不要将此工具与 :doc:`这个页面 </modeling/meshes/editing/smoothing>` 提到"
"的着色平滑选项混淆，二者的原理并不相同！此工具通过修改网格本身来降低其尖"
"锐程度，然而 *设置光滑* / *自动光滑* 只是通过控制网格的着色方式，来产生柔"
"和的 *错觉*，但其实并没有修改网格。"
